If the rest of the class is required to use a specific type of calculator, please specify below: *  RequiredAre there any course specific materials required or allowed for this exam? If yes, please specify. (i.e. model kits, formula sheets, reference texts, etc.)YesNoPlease specify what notes are allowed. (i.e. number of pages, one or two sided, note cards, written, typed, etc) *  RequiredCollect all notes when student turns in exam/quiz?YesNoSpecify:How do you want the exam returned? *  RequiredScannedPick UpStudent Uploads to Gradescope or submits via Blackboard or Examsoft (please specify in notes section below)List the email address(es) below to send the completed exam back. *  RequiredSpecify who will be allowed to pick up the exam. *  RequiredThe individual will need to present ID and sign a form confirming receipt.Comments:Send ExamPlease email the exam to accesstesting@uic.edu at your earliest convenience or upload with this form. 

 If one proctor form will be used for the entire semester, please skip this section and email exams directly to accesstesting@uic.edu prior to each exam or quiz with the exam/quiz number, as well as course name and number in the subject line. File

